```graphql
query deployment($id: String!) {
  deployment(id: $id) {
    id
    status
    createdAt
    url
    staticUrl
    meta
    canRedeploy
    canRollback
  }
}
```

### Get Latest Active Deployment
```graphql
query latestDeployment($input: DeploymentListInput!) {
  deployments(input: $input, first: 1) {
    edges {
      node {
        id
        status
        url
        createdAt
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### Get Build Logs
